programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Mr Bean and his beloved car find themselves in a crash for crash battle with his arch nemesis the Reliant Robin. It’s a contest to find out who can hold their nerve the longest. Does Mr Bean win? Is his car left unscathed? And more importantly do we find out who the driver of the Reliant Robin really is?

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Mr Bean has got everything ready for Irma’s birthday; card cake candles but he just needs to get her some flowers. But nothing goes to plan as Mr Bean inadvertently causes a car crash involving a bride on her wedding day. There’s no time to lose as Mr Bean promises he’ll get the bride to the church on time. Irma is not a happy lady as Mr Bean is distracted by the task in hand.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Mr Bean sees a new toy car in the window of the local department store Havlotts and decides he must have it. But on the way to the toy department Mr Bean gets stuck in the lift. He tries his best to entertain his fellow passengers but they aren’t very appreciative. How can Mr Bean resolve the situation and get the toy he so desperately wants?

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: It is a nice sunny day and Mr. Bean and Mrs. Wicket are relaxing in the garden, Mr. Bean attempts to sit beside her in the cool shade of her outdoor umbrella but Mrs. Wicket refuses. He decides to design his own umbrella for himself and Teddy. As he starts digging, he discovers - to his surprise - a bomb. He tries to disarm it, unfortunately, his attempt only accelerates its countdown.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Mr Bean goes to the theatre to see a performance by a celebrated hypnotist Dr Daze. Bean is super keen to come up on stage and be part of the show. But after being hypnotized Bean unknowingly leaves the theatre not realizing that he is still under the influence and certain trigger sounds have him doing silly things at unexpected and embarrassing moments.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: After a stubborn bird deliberately defecates his Mini, Mr. Bean washes it. After the passing motorist mistakenly thinks that Bean runs a car wash, Bean makes some makeshift car washing equipment at the side of the road. Mrs. Wicket joins Bean by offering tea to the motorist. Soon after, Bean is washing cars that belong to the Royal Queen but the same bird defecates on the car.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Mr Bean chases Scrapper around Mrs Wickets flat but her sideboard tumbles over, and when Bean sees a bit of fur poking out from under it, he is horrified to think he has squashed poor Scrapper. Not realising that it is only his landladys furry hat, Bean rushes what he thinks is a flattened cat across town to the vet in a desperate attempt to save his feline friends life.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Mr Bean plays gooseberry when Mrs Wicket falls in love with a man Mr Bean doesn’t trust.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Mr Bean fancies a game of golf so he creates his own golf course inside his flat and invites Irma to join him for a round. Their somewhat eccentric game takes them from sitting room to bathroom and through Mrs Wicket’s flat as they battle to be the winner of the First Bean Open Championship.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Mr. Bean gets in a flap when a monster turns up in his cake-mix. The good news, though, is that the monster turns out to be a harmless baby bird. The bad news is that it grows into a huge stork and takes over his home. Bean attempts to return it to the wild, and finds teaching it to fly makes his arms ache.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: When the frogspawn in Mr. Bean’s bath hatch out, it’s the last thing his landlady needs, especially when she’s invited the Mayor for tea. Hundreds of angry amphibians decide to invite themselves as well. Bean proves to be no expert at catching slippery green things that won’t stop hopping about all over the blinking place.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Mr. Bean meets an aristocratic old lady when he nearly runs over her lapdog with his mini. Hes thrilled to be invited for luncheon at her grand but strangely shabby mansion. Bean is determined to rise to the occasion. Hes so busy with matters of protocol he doesnt notice that the lady and her sinister butler arent quite what they seem...

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: How does one choose tasteful wallpaper these days? After watching a royal documentary on TV, Mr. Bean decides to decorate his room in the style of Buckingham Palace. If the Queen’s new wallpaper is good enough for Her Royal Highness, then it’s going to be good enough for him. Meanwhile, his landlady, Mrs. Wicket, suffers from illusions of grandeur and crowns herself Queen of the street.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Mr. Bean finds himself in a race to grow a giant marrow with his next-door neighbour. There’s prize money at stake and a chance to get his photo in the papers. And so, as the competition gets tough, Bean’s gardening techniques become more ingenious, unconventional and desperate.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: He’s got her record, the poster and the T-shirt, so when Mr. Bean’s heart-throb, Roxy, is set to sing in concert at the London Palladium, he sets his sights on the only thing that will make his life complete: her signature in his autograph book. A difficult feat but can love prevail?

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Mr. Bean is over the moon when he meets Mr. Pod because both men have so much in common; same shirt, jacket, trousers and underpants. And to top it all, Pod is Bean’s spitting image! Bean falls to Earth with a bump, though, when his girlfriend, Irma Gobb, finds Mr. Pod much better looking than him.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Inspired by a wildlife documentary on TV, Mr. Bean dusts off his camera and treks deep into the countryside in search of the perfect wildlife photograph. After two fruitless days of being the hunter, he is somewhat miffed to find himself the hunted.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Whilst browsing the supermarket for lovely grub, Mr. Bean’s life-long pal, Teddy, is kidnapped. Bean tracks down the nasty men responsible and finds that Teddy is not their only captive. Mr. Bean rescues a hundred teddy bears once their ears are put through an industrial sewing machine.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Mr Bean is furious with the untidy state of the streets and all the people who drop litter so he goes on a one-man mission to clean up the town. Armed with several bin bags Mr Bean collects all the rubbish and puts up his own ‘No Littering’ signs - which have absolutely no effect. When the police show no interest in his campaign Bean builds a homemade vacuuming contraption causing chaos and mayhem wherever he goes.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Mr Bean decides to do something romantic on Valentine’s Day for his long-suffering girlfriend Irma. But while he is secretly delivering her valentines card Mr Bean finds out he has a love rival for Irma’s attention. Bean steps up his efforts and takes Irma on a ‘date’ to the Valentine’s Fair only to find his love rival is there too! But will the fortune-teller’s prediction be the ticket to a happy ending?

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Mr Bean has forgotten hes supposed to be cooking dinner for his long-suffering girlfriend Irma. He dashes to the supermarket to buy some groceries but why buy food when you can win an entire trolley full in an All You Can Eat Competition? But Mr Bean has some stiff competition - no one can eat one of Mr Magg’s pies quicker than Mr Maggs himself. Mr Bean has to think fast to win. But after all that eating will Bean still be in the mood to cook a romantic meal?

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Mr Bean is in need of a sturdy new bookcase and sets off to visit a furniture warehouse. He finds one that’s perfect but is outraged when he’s told he has to build the bookcase himself! Bean is unfamiliar with flat pack assembly and struggles to construct his new bookcase failing miserably when he discovers he’s one screw short. Mr Bean heads back to the shop only to find it’s closed!

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Mr Bean decides to take Teddy on holiday to the seaside. But when he arrives at his hotel a spoilt little girl wants Teddy all for herself. And her protective dad only wants the best for his ‘princess’. An on-going tussle ensues between Mr Bean the little girl and her Dad resulting in a chase across the seaside town and onto the pier. No one comes between Mr Bean Teddy and their ‘relaxing’ holiday!

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Mr Bean is left in peace when Mrs Wicket goes off on her holidays. This means Mr Bean has free access to her daily newspaper. But every time he goes down to collect it from the letterbox it disappears. Someone is taking it but who? Mr Bean is determined to nab the mysterious newspaper stealer and uses a range of ingenious homemade traps in his quest to catch the sneaky thief.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Mr Bean is trying to find a nice quiet place to read his book so he sets off for the Library. But instead of reading he becomes distracted by some funny online videos he sees on the Librarys computer. Before he knows it Mr Bean is recording his own video which is uploaded for everyone to see. Things start to go crazy when people check out his funny video and his popularity takes off. But does Mr Bean enjoy being in the public eye and how long will his celebrity last?

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Mr Bean is obsessed by his favourite TV hero ‘Super Spy’ and is excited when his very own Super-Spy spy kit arrives in the post. While Mr Bean is pretending to be his favourite character and delighting in all his gadgets he spots some unusual goings on in the Bruisers’ house next door. Naturally Mr Bean assumes the worst and sets out to rectify the situation.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Mr Bean becomes scoutmaster for the day, but his obsession with badge collecting does not help him make friends.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: When did Mr. Bean first meet his teddy bear? Did he really learn to drive his mini at the age of ten? Could he possibly have known his battle-axe of a landlady when she was a sweet and blushing bride? Bean takes us on a journey into the past, answering these questions and giving us an inkling as to what made him the man he is today.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Mr. Bean finds himself lumbered with an unwanted pet in the form of a four-legged ball of pink fur with piggy eyes and a penchant for earthworms. Encyclopedias leave him none the wiser as to the identity of the pesky creature but Bean can’t bring himself to just abandon it. The puzzle is eventually solved after a picnic in the park and a raid on the local pet shop.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Mr. Bean forgets the golden rule: never fall asleep in the bath when youve got a chicken in the oven. So what romantic meal can he quickly rustle-up for his luckless girlfriend, Irma Gobb? The cheese from the mousetrap? The flower from the vase? A meal is eventually provided by an uninvited guest.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: The nasty tennis player is big and angry and wants his ball back. The one Mr. Bean managed to throw on the roof of a house across the road. Paralysed with vertigo sixty feet up on a windowsill, he is eventually brought to earth by the helpful intervention of a neighbour’s pet gerbil.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Eating too many sweets gives Bean a terrible toothache, and when all other attempts at curing it are exhausted, he reluctantly visits the dreaded dentist.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: After (accidentally) rescuing a kitten from a tree Mr. Bean is set to have his picture in the newspaper! The photographer arrives with the grateful lady cat owner, the scene is set, smiles all round…but then disaster strikes when Bean is continually upstaged by… his hair.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: As Mr Bean settles down to watch his favourite TV programme he hears loud noises from next-door. He moves from house to garden but can’t escape the relentless cacophony of trumpets, electric drills, and screaming babies. Bean’s mind turns to thoughts of revenge….

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Envious of all the attention his landlady is receiving because of a broken leg, Mr. Bean decides to break his leg too. When he ends up in hospital under the care of the Matron from Hell he discovers there are some kinds of attention even he doesnt enjoy.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Whilst trying to redecorate the hall, Bean is obstructed at every turn by his landlady’s vile one-eyed cat. Bean pops it in the dustbin to keep it out of the way for a while. Just his luck that it’s rubbish collection day.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Mr Bean and Irma are off for a day at the seaside. Irma is travelling light but Bean wants to take almost everything his owns in an enormous trunk. Arriving at the seaside Bean’s trunk gets accidentally swapped with a trunk belonging to a famous stage magician. As Bean entertains Irma pulling rabbits out of hats the angry magician arrives on the scene - and he’s not a happy bunny.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Mr Bean loves playing in the neighbourhood soft play centre – bouncing on the trampolines whizzing down the slides and most of all immersing himself in the ball pool. But he doesn’t like sharing the place with all those annoying kids. So Bean decides to turn his flat into his own private play area where he can play in peace. Unfortunately Irma Mrs Wicket and The Bruisers all want to join in the fun with him.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Mr Bean orders a takeaway pizza but when it arrives he feels let down by the size of it. So he sets out to bake his own unique Teddy shaped pizzas. Under the name Pizza Bean his pizzas become extremely popular and very soon business in booming. As a result rival pizza producer Don Crustyoni sees his profits plummeting and decides to make Mr Bean an offer he can’t refuse.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Mr Bean is not allowed to fly off on holiday as his passport has no photograph. After failing to get one from a photo booth he tries numerous other ways to get his photo taken including photobombing a tourist’s snap. None of these work but after Bean is arrested maybe the police can assist him. Say cheese!

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Mr Bean wants to impress Irma by entering them both into a dance competition at the local park. But his tango is terrible and his rumba ridiculous so he enrols for lessons at a local dance school. After an unsuccessful class at the dance studio and a trip to the library to teach himself Mr Bean has lost track of time. He needs to make it up to a disgruntled Irma but will his homemade effort ‘win’ her over.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Mr Bean manages to get himself locked in a department store overnight while spending too long trying on clothes. Bean takes advantage of the situation having fun in the various departments. But when he discovers a robbery taking place the fun and games stop as the desperate burglar chases Bean from floor to floor and all around the store.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Mr. Bean becomes obsessed with gaming after being introduced by Mrs. Wickets nephew. He decides he must have his own console, only to discover how expensive they are. But as luck would have it, he arrives at the shop at closing time to discover that tomorrow there will be a special sale. All he has to do is be first in line.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Mrs. Wicket demands that Bean stay in to take delivery of a new lounge chair.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Mr Bean dog-sits for Irma and while in the park comes across a professional dog-walker. This guy’s making a fortune while Bean is doing it for free! That evening posters go up and the next morning Bean has four dogs to look after. But who is going to walk whom?

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Nipping to the shops for a few provisions becomes a nightmare when a mile-long shopping list from his landlady and a clapped out trolley with a wonky wheel conspire to ruin his day. Subscribing to the theory that bigger is better, he constructs his own shopping trolley incorporating a petrol mower, pram wheels and an extra pair of hydraulic hands.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: When nursing an injured magpie in his room, Mr. Bean learns something the rest of us already know: magpies can’t help stealing anything that sparkles. When the police arrive to investigate the theft of his landlady’s jewellery, it’s not just Mr. Bean that needs to take flight.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: After a head-on collision with the milkman, Mr. Bean’s landlady is rushed to hospital, leaving him to look after her odious one-eyed cat Scrapper. Fur isn’t the only thing that flies and in the end it’s Bean that needs looking after.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Mr. Bean is delighted with his new ‘ship in a bottle’ until it mistakenly ends up on a milkman’s float. He frantically pursues his prize possession, only to see it disappear into a milk bottling plant at the local dairy. Getting it back promises to be a mission of the impossible.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: With his teddy bear at the dry cleaners, Mr. Bean finds himself feeling lonely. Fortunately, a new playmate appears in the shape of a goldfish from the garden pond. Bean has a great time with his new best friend until, at the seaside, he discovers that some fish are gigantic, have large pointed teeth and fins on their backs.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: When Mr. Wicket gets a new lodger who isan Inventor, and a big nuisance, Bean discovers that he has to become inventive himself. But, when your enemy is clever and sneaky, you have to be even cleverer and sneakier. Bean has never lost a cleverness competition, but maybe there is a first time for everything!

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Conned by a mechanic into believing his beloved car to be beyond repair, Mr. Bean reluctantly consigns his faithful four-wheeled friend to the car crusher. After choosing hot-air ballooning as an alternative mode of transport, he spots his cherished car from the air… with the unscrupulous mechanic whistling at the wheel! This discovery raises more than Mr. Bean’s spirits.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Mr. Bean’s Birthday dinner gets off on the wrong foot when he and Teddy are made to take the worst table at a swanky restaurant. The evening is further ruined by a self-obsessed movie star at the next table. After a swim in the lobster tank, Mr. Bean unwittingly cooks up sweet revenge in the kitchen.

This discovery raises more than Mr. Bean’s spirits.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Mr. Bean accidentally spills all of Mrs. Wickets new, expensive perfume on the floor. He might be able to fool Mrs. Wicket, but can he fool Scrapper and all the neighbourhood cats?

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Mr Bean drives his favourite Teddy to the cinema to see his favourite movie - Titanic. Now he simply has to park the car. But when youre Mr Bean, nothings simple. His ingenious efforts to find a parking space are persistently foiled. And the clock is ticking....

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: A local archaeology dig inspires Bean to go in search of treasure. But why buy a metal detector when you can make one from lawnmower parts and a dustbin lid? However, his happiness is soon thwarted by the arrival of two baddies, the police and a very angry Landlady.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: There’s easy money to be had in the art world and Mr. Bean is set on getting some of it. Once equipped with the right tools, he ventures into the countryside with a blank canvas in search of inspiration – and comes home with a painting full of life. Literally.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: When Mr. Bean finds a fly in his room, its war. He needs weapons. Fly spray? A rolled-up magazine? These are only the start. In desperation, he enlists a mouldy doughnut, an encyclopaedia, an upside-down dustbin and a club-hammer. Finally, Bean becomes the first man in history to wage war on a fly... with a fridge.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: A leisurely stroll in the park turns into a run when Mr. Bean is chased home by an angry Mime Artist. He is lost for more words than usual when the street performer makes himself at home and insists on being wined and dined. Bean ousts the pest from his house using the only language mime artists understand.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Chaotic cartoon capers following the further adventures of the popular halfwit immortalised in the live-action TV series and Hollywood films. With the voice of Rowan Atkinson.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Sometimes Mr. Bean’s Teddy can be no fun at all. Feeling the need for a new friend, Bean buys a parrot. But getting the parrot past his landlady and her one-eyed cat, Scrapper, proves to be no easy task. Next, is trying to get the blasted bird to speak.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: It’s a beautiful day at the beach. Bean breathes in the salty air, bliss - and not another soul in sight. What could possibly spoil his perfect day? Answer: British weather. Mr. Bean finds himself chasing an illusive ray of sunshine across town, over hills and dales, a football stadium and the English Channel.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Mr. Bean is shocked when Teddy receives a birthday card from Bean’s girlfriend, Irma Gobb. The bear’s Birthday had completely slipped his mind. And what do you get for the teddy that has everything? A morning in a toy shop, burgers for lunch and a slap up tea party, of course. (But only if you can afford it.)

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: When theres no milk for his tea and for Teddy, Mr. Bean goes to buy some. However, instead of parking near the grocery store because of the traffic warden, he parks his car at a nearby school where he is mistaken by the principal as the new teacher and is forced to teach a group of juvenile delinquents. But he actually may be a better teacher than he thought.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Mr Bean is in the library studying his family heritage. Someone brings to his attention Mr Bean’s resemblance to a certain Lord Bean. Mr Bean sets off to track down his ancestral home (a castle) in Scotland where he is welcomed with open arms. But owning a castle is not cheap. Can Mr Bean escape before he runs out of money and has there been a case of mistaken identity?

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Mr Bean and his beloved car find themselves in a crash for crash battle with his arch nemesis the Reliant Robin. It’s a contest to find out who can hold their nerve the longest. Does Mr Bean win? Is his car left unscathed? And more importantly do we find out who the driver of the Reliant Robin really is?

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Mr Bean has got everything ready for Irma’s birthday; card cake candles but he just needs to get her some flowers. But nothing goes to plan as Mr Bean inadvertently causes a car crash involving a bride on her wedding day. There’s no time to lose as Mr Bean promises he’ll get the bride to the church on time. Irma is not a happy lady as Mr Bean is distracted by the task in hand.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Mr Bean is keen to own a brand new smart phone when he discovers all the wonderful things it can do. But after a trip to the mobile phone shop he is horrified at how much they cost and decides to build his own one. Bean’s phone may be bulky but it comes with a whole range of built in gadgets especially useful during a race to The Tower of London.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: A confused Japanese tourist couple mistake Mr Bean’s house for a hotel and because of the language barrier it is difficult to explain otherwise. When the hapless holidaymakers offer to pay to stay Mr Bean and Mrs Wicket see a way of making some money and pretend their house is indeed a hotel. But it’s not long before the tourists start to smell a fish.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: While Mr. Bean is taking photos of wildlife, he sees big footprints belonging to a dinosaur. He starts running away but then gets an idea to take a photo of these footprints, hoping hell become famous. However, the dinosaur turns out to be part of a set for a movie called Jurassic Hero and Bean is added to the cast.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Mr Bean accidently causes Mrs Wicket to be hospitalised and in need of a wheelchair. Back home Mr Bean has thoughtfully set up a bell service so that he can be at Mrs Wicket’s beck and call at any time of day or night. Mrs Wicket likes this...a lot. The bell doesn’t stop ringing and an exhausted Mr Bean finds himself running up and down the stairs carrying and fetching until he eventually loses patience with his patient.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Mr Bean’s car has broken down and he is late to meet Irma for a night at the opera. Mr Bean finally arrives but he is refused entry to the theatre because of his filthy attire. Forced to borrow some clothes from the local launderette Bean is mistaken for the star of the show and ends up on the stage giving the operatic performance of a lifetime.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: During a visit to Londons National Gallery, Bean witnesses the theft of a major work of art.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Whos afraid of silent movies about killer cats, alien blobs, and little men dancing in sugar bowls? Mr Bean. He is very scared. A trip to the cinema sends his imagination running wild.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Against his better judgement, Bean has agreed to go out on a proper date with Irma Gobb, his girlfriend. She has the perfect evening planned: a romantic film followed by a candlelit dinner for two. If only she had the perfect boyfriend to go with it.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Mistaken for an escaped convict, Bean is carted off to jail where he finds that, with a little imagination, prison can be quite nice actually. The real convict finds life less cosy under the thumb of Mr. Bean’s landlady.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Mr. Bean finds himself dogged by a young Japanese boy at the Science Museum. He takes an instant dislike to the Scallywag until he sees what the kid has in his backpack: gadgets so cool you cant even get them in the West. So when a security guard tries to ruin their fun they run away together to... Mars!

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Mr. Bean cannot, for the life of him, place the face of the uninvited fat bloke on his doorstep. An old school photograph and school cap just about jog his memory. By this time his new ‘friend’ has put his feet up and is eating Bean out of house and home. This blast from the past proves to be a blasted pain in the neck.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Irma Gobb comes round to watch TV and Bean finds that liking different programmes to your girlfriend can be very bad for a relationship. After an explosive argument the TV blows up, forcing Mr. Bean to invent his own very ingenious form of home entertainment.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Mr. Bean would like to learn to play a Beethoven symphony, so he arranges a piano, a music book, a candlestick and a very patient piano teacher. It can be done this way too, Liberace!

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Its the start of a Fun Run. Mr. Bean lines-up beside his deadly enemy: the fat bloke who stole his parking space. Fun Run or no, nothing will stop Bean beating this man to the finishing post, even if he has to flag a cab.

programme.desc: Mr Bean buys a robot to clean his flat but it ends up trashing half the town.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Mr Bean wants an ice cream from the ice cream van but ends up serving himself – along with every kid in town.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Mr Bean is feeling very left out when he discovers that Mrs Wicket is having a huge party downstairs and apparently he isnt invited. Bean tries every trick in the book to sneak himself into the party - even resorting to hiding inside an enormous cake. If only he knew the real reason for the celebration.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Mr Bean’s attempt to cut the grass is thwarted by a pesky root which refuses to budge. When Mr Bean breaks his spade he heads to the local Garden Centre to find a replacement. But instead of simply buying one he enters a gardening competition to win one - judged by none other than the Queen herself! Its gardening gloves off when Mr Bean goes into battle with his rival green-fingered competitors.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Mr Bean and Irma are off for a day at the seaside. Irma is travelling light but Bean wants to take almost everything his owns in an enormous trunk. Arriving at the seaside Bean’s trunk gets accidentally swapped with a trunk belonging to a famous stage magician. As Bean entertains Irma pulling rabbits out of hats the angry magician arrives on the scene - and he’s not a happy bunny.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Mr Bean loves playing in the neighbourhood soft play centre – bouncing on the trampolines whizzing down the slides and most of all immersing himself in the ball pool. But he doesn’t like sharing the place with all those annoying kids. So Bean decides to turn his flat into his own private play area where he can play in peace. Unfortunately Irma Mrs Wicket and The Bruisers all want to join in the fun with him.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Mr Bean orders a takeaway pizza but when it arrives he feels let down by the size of it. So he sets out to bake his own unique Teddy shaped pizzas. Under the name Pizza Bean his pizzas become extremely popular and very soon business in booming. As a result rival pizza producer Don Crustyoni sees his profits plummeting and decides to make Mr Bean an offer he can’t refuse.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Mr Bean is not allowed to fly off on holiday as his passport has no photograph. After failing to get one from a photo booth he tries numerous other ways to get his photo taken including photobombing a tourist’s snap. None of these work but after Bean is arrested maybe the police can assist him. Say cheese!

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Mr Bean wants to impress Irma by entering them both into a dance competition at the local park. But his tango is terrible and his rumba ridiculous so he enrols for lessons at a local dance school. After an unsuccessful class at the dance studio and a trip to the library to teach himself Mr Bean has lost track of time. He needs to make it up to a disgruntled Irma but will his homemade effort ‘win’ her over.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Nipping to the shops for a few provisions becomes a nightmare when a mile-long shopping list from his landlady and a clapped out trolley with a wonky wheel conspire to ruin his day. Subscribing to the theory that bigger is better, he constructs his own shopping trolley incorporating a petrol mower, pram wheels and an extra pair of hydraulic hands.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: When nursing an injured magpie in his room, Mr. Bean learns something the rest of us already know: magpies can’t help stealing anything that sparkles. When the police arrive to investigate the theft of his landlady’s jewellery, it’s not just Mr. Bean that needs to take flight.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: After a head-on collision with the milkman, Mr. Bean’s landlady is rushed to hospital, leaving him to look after her odious one-eyed cat Scrapper. Fur isn’t the only thing that flies and in the end it’s Bean that needs looking after.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Mr. Bean is delighted with his new ‘ship in a bottle’ until it mistakenly ends up on a milkman’s float. He frantically pursues his prize possession, only to see it disappear into a milk bottling plant at the local dairy. Getting it back promises to be a mission of the impossible.

programme.desc: A local archaeology dig inspires Bean to go in search of treasure. But why buy a metal detector when you can make one from lawnmower parts and a dustbin lid? After destroying his landlady’s back garden, Mr. Bean tries out his hand-made contraption in the woods. He is overjoyed to discover a buried chest of gold doubloons. However, his happiness is soon thwarted by the arrival of two baddies, the police and a very angry Landlady.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: There’s easy money to be had in the art world and Mr. Bean is set on getting some of it. Once equipped with the right tools, he ventures into the countryside with a blank canvas in search of inspiration – and comes home with a painting full of life. Literally.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: When Mr. Bean finds a fly in his room, its war. He needs weapons. Fly spray? A rolled-up magazine? These are only the start. In desperation, he enlists a mouldy doughnut, an encyclopaedia, an upside-down dustbin and a club-hammer. Finally, Bean becomes the first man in history to wage war on a fly... with a fridge.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: A leisurely stroll in the park turns into a run when Mr. Bean is chased home by an angry Mime Artist. He is lost for more words than usual when the street performer makes himself at home and insists on being wined and dined. Bean ousts the pest from his house using the only language mime artists understand.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Chaotic cartoon capers following the further adventures of the popular halfwit immortalised in the live-action TV series and Hollywood films. With the voice of Rowan Atkinson.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Sometimes Mr. Bean’s Teddy can be no fun at all. Feeling the need for a new friend, Bean buys a parrot. But getting the parrot past his landlady and her one-eyed cat, Scrapper, proves to be no easy task. Next, is trying to get the blasted bird to speak.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: It’s a beautiful day at the beach. Bean breathes in the salty air, bliss - and not another soul in sight. What could possibly spoil his perfect day? Answer: British weather. Mr. Bean finds himself chasing an illusive ray of sunshine across town, over hills and dales, a football stadium and the English Channel.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Mr. Bean is shocked when Teddy receives a birthday card from Bean’s girlfriend, Irma Gobb. The bear’s Birthday had completely slipped his mind. And what do you get for the teddy that has everything? A morning in a toy shop, burgers for lunch and a slap up tea party, of course. (But only if you can afford it.)

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: It is a nice sunny day and Mr. Bean and Mrs. Wicket are relaxing in the garden, Mr. Bean attempts to sit beside her in the cool shade of her outdoor umbrella but Mrs. Wicket refuses. He decides to design his own umbrella for himself and Teddy. As he starts digging, he discovers - to his surprise - a bomb. He tries to disarm it, unfortunately, his attempt only accelerates its countdown.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Mr Bean goes to the theatre to see a performance by a celebrated hypnotist Dr Daze. Bean is super keen to come up on stage and be part of the show. But after being hypnotized Bean unknowingly leaves the theatre not realizing that he is still under the influence and certain trigger sounds have him doing silly things at unexpected and embarrassing moments.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: After a stubborn bird deliberately defecates his Mini, Mr. Bean washes it. After the passing motorist mistakenly thinks that Bean runs a car wash, Bean makes some makeshift car washing equipment at the side of the road. Mrs. Wicket joins Bean by offering tea to the motorist. Soon after, Bean is washing cars that belong to the Royal Queen but the same bird defecates on the car.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Mr Bean chases Scrapper around Mrs Wickets flat but her sideboard tumbles over, and when Bean sees a bit of fur poking out from under it, he is horrified to think he has squashed poor Scrapper. Not realising that it is only his landladys furry hat, Bean rushes what he thinks is a flattened cat across town to the vet in a desperate attempt to save his feline friends life.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Mr Bean plays gooseberry when Mrs Wicket falls in love with a man Mr Bean doesn’t trust.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Mr Bean loves Halloween and prepares to give the neighbourhood kids some tricks and treats they won’t forget. But when Mr Bean gets carried away with his spooky pranks he becomes the target of even more fiendish tricks from his neighbours the Bruisers.

programme.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
programme.desc: Mr Bean is painting a picture of Teddy when he accidently squirts some green paint onto his brown wallpaper. Oh no! Bean needs to redecorate his room fast but ends up painting all the walls a garish lime green instead of brown. He’s so terrified of Mrs Wicket finding out that when he goes to bed he has some very weird nightmares – with a rather sickly ending.

programme.title: Queen of Fucking Everything
programme.desc: Linda ja Marke sõidavad Hispaaniasse ning Marke saab teada reisi tõelise eesmargi. Marke edutatakse Linda remondifirma Queen of Homes tegevdirektoriks. Linda kohtub Koistise naisena esinedes Hispaania ostjaga. Kodumaal puuab Koistinen kadunud kauba jalgi ajada ja salaparases tehingus selgust saada. programme.title: Heartbeat

programme.title: Superkangelased
programme.desc: See on uhe paari lugu - impulsiivse ja mittekonformistliku iseloomuga karikaturist Anna ja fuusikaõpetaja Marco, kes on veendunud, et kõik siin elus on juhitud valemite jargi. Nad on erinevad, aga ometi koos. Annal tuleb idee teha koomiks paaridest, keda ta nimetab superkangelasteks, sest selleks, et kaua koos olla ja uksteist vaatamata kõigele armastada, on vaja supervõimeid! Režissoor Paolo Genovese sai vaatajatele tuntuks filmiga „Taiuslikud võõrad“, mis osutus suureks hitiks nii Eestis kui ka mujal riikides.

programme.title: Osoon
programme.desc: Tallinna Tehnikaulikooli teadlaste kutsel kais sel suvel Eestis tunnustatud Briti loodusfotograaf ja allveefilmija Jack Perks, kes on hindamatu spetsialist kalade filmimise alal. Kohtume Perksiga Pirita jõel, kus ta Eesti teadusruhma nõustab. Eesti on hiljuti saanud rikkamaks uhe orhideeliigi võrra. Meil on eriline võimalus naha seda salajases paigas kasvavat kapalist nimega sale tanukeel, mis on võetud range kaitse alla. Kaido Haageni luhilugu viib meid inimese poolt asustamata Kuningakulla, kus kaib siiski vilgas elu. Saate autorid on Kristo Elias ja Sander Loite, toimetaja Marit Valk, režissoor Keiti Valiste, produtsent Heiki Sepp.

programme.title: Tooroobikud
programme.desc: Lisaks inimestele ruhmavad ka mitmed neljajalgsed sõbrad paevast paeva tood teha. Naiteks politseikoerad, kes aitavad korravalvuritel kurikaelu puuda või juhtkoerad, kelle ulesandeks on erivajadustega inimestele abiks olla. Sel nadalal satime end toovarjuks Enele ja Anule, kes tormakatest kutsikatest tublid tooloomad kasvatavad. Režissoor Marten Vaher, autor-toimetaja Marit Ummelas, produtsent Hannela Lippus.

programme.title: Heureka
programme.desc: Selleks hetkeks kui kardinad avanevad ja sinu ette kerkib etenduse maailm, on iga detail paigas. Lavastus ei sunni sel õhtul kohapeal ja sinu kustumatu teatrielamuse nimel on teinud kuude kaupa kõvasti tood vaga suur meeskond. Laheme avastama, mis toimub kulisside taga ja kes tootavad teatri koogipoolel. Jalgime muusikali „Huljatud” valmimise protsessi Vanemuise teatris. Tootja Downtown Pictures OÜ.

programme.title: Lahutus Eesti moodi
programme.desc: Tauno rahakraanide sulgumine seab Aksli ja Laura pulmaplaanid uuesti ohtu. Tagasi tulnud Mirjam peab nuud selgusele jõudma, kas ta tahab elada ka vaese Taunoga. Laural tuleb koos enda uue pagaripoisiga idee, kuidas salakavalale konkurendile ara teha – Richard nõuab Lauralt uhte romantilist ood hotellis, et siis naise pagariari rahule jatta. Laura otsustab pagaripoiss Dani abiga mehele lõksu seada ja asjad võtavad nuud taiesti poorase poorde. Stsenarist Martin Algus, režissoor Ergo Kuld, tootja Kassikuld OÜ.

programme.title: Aeg õppida
programme.desc: Tartumaa aasta õppija Meelis maletab selgelt, kuidas õpetaja põhikoolis utles, et sellest poisist asja ei saa. Aga sai. Meelis tegi teoks oma unistuse inimesi aidata ja tootab tana nii kiirabis kui ka paastekomandos. Raplamaa ettevõtja Maria sukeldus parast keskkooli turismi ja turunduse valdkonda, aga taipas uhel hetkel, et see too ei ole talle ning hakkas leiba teenima hoopis keraamikuna. Kolme lapse emana otsustas ta tanavu uuesti õppima asuda, sel korral kutsekooli, sest tal on oma karjaari osas selged plaanid. Režissoor Andres Lepasar, toimetaja Mari Tamm, produtsent Lii Kuldmae.

programme.title: Õnne 13
programme.desc: Are saab teada, et Taivo elab koos Anneliga. Mats toob oma pruudi Brita Uuevarikult Annemaid ja Intsu kulastama. Laine ja Alma lasevad Haraldil enda eest hoolitseda. Oliver-Sten ja Merilin raagivad Maigele suuri uudiseid.

programme.title: Maahommik
programme.desc: "Maahommik" randab mooda Eestimaad ringi ja kohtub erinevate inimeste ja nende põnevate tegemistega. Teie ees rullub lahti maaelu varvipalett koos kõikide oma varjunditega. Loomad, taimed, talud, tood ja musttuhat muud lugu ootab teid just "Maahommiku" saates. Saatejuht on Kerli Dello. Vastutav toimetaja Maili Metssalu, režissoorid Mikk Mae ja Mati Kark, produtsent Tiina-Mari Koljak.

programme.title: Puudutus
programme.desc: 1944. aasta sugisel peavad tuhanded eestlased jatma oma kodu ja põgenema ule mere tundmatusse. Nuud, 80 aastat hiljem, avatakse Parnus sellele traagilisele sundmusele puhendatud malestusmark. Varskes dokumentaalfilmis saavad sõna skulptor Elo Liiv ja eestlased nii lahedalt kui ka kaugelt. Režissoor Marko Piirsoo, produtsent Kaidor Kahar, tootja Suur Pilt OÜ.

programme.title: Pealtnagija
programme.desc: "Pealtnagija" on Eesti pikima ajalooga ja teletabelite tipus olev uuriv ajakirjandussaade, mis toob vaatajateni põnevad ja paljastavad lood meie uhiskonna telgitagustest. Lisaks teravatele uurimustele vahendab saade ka haaravaid persoone ja meeldejaavaid reportaaže sundmustest, mille pealtnagijaks tavaline inimene naljalt ei satu. Saatejuhid Mihkel Karmas, Kristjan Pihl, Merilin Parli, Taavi Eilat ja Margit Kilumets. Režissoorid Raivo Maripuu ja Vladlen Pobjaržin, produtsent Piret Priisaar.

programme.title: Kirjandusministri juures. Muusika eri
programme.desc: Raamatuaasta puhul võõrustab kirjandusminister Mart Juur Eesti raamat 500 patrooni, president Alar Karist. Kord kuus raagime presidendi jaoks olulistest teostest. Tana kasitleme koos presidendi ja kulalistega Maarja Unduski raamatut "Ellen Niit. Heleda mõtte laast".

programme.title: Eesti Muusika- ja Teatriakadeemia 100. Ajaloost ja inimestest
programme.desc: 1919. aasta septebrikuus asus 412 ettevõtlikku noort inimest õppima Tallinna Kõrgemasse Muusikakooli. Saja aastaga on sellest koolist kujunenud uhke ajaloo ja uhiuue saaliga Eesti Teatri- ja Muusikaakadeemia. Kes olid need inimesed, kes sellele koolile aluse panid ja mis on see jõud, mis inimesi muusika juurde toob, raagivad Gustav Ernesaks, Hugo Lepnurm, Villem Reimann, Eugen Kapp, Veera Lensin, Tiit Kuusik jt. Režissoor Ülle Õun, produtsent Ruth Alakula.

programme.title: Hercule Poirot
programme.desc: Masinakirjutaja kutsutakse kindlaks kellaajaks teatud aadressile. Perenaist pole kusagil, maja on tais kellasid, mis naitavad vale aega, ja tagatipuks lamab diivani taga tundmatu surnukeha. Juhuslikult sinna kanti sattunud leitnant palub Poirot appi, kuna on veendunud tutarlapse suutuses.

programme.title: September
programme.desc: 1944. aasta septembris evakueeruvad sakslased kiirkorras Tallinnast, samal ajal laheneb linnale Punaarmee. Sooviga Eesti iseseisvus taastada, naaseb Vello Salo koos teiste soomepoistega kuu aega varem Eestisse. Jaan Kross on juba pool aastat sakslaste kaes vangis olnud, suudistuseks koostoo põrandaaluste iseseisvuslastega. Malestuste ja intervjuude põhjal jutustab film loo viiest keerulisest paevast 1944. aasta septembris. Autorid Ilmar Raag ja Kiur Aarma. Tootja Traumfabrik OÜ.

programme.title: Torm
programme.desc: Hadaolukord ei huua tulles – olgu selleks siis torm, uleujutus, elektrikatkestus või midagi hoopis muud. Filmi peategelaseks on pereisa, kes otsustabki uhel paeval ootamatusteks valmistuma hakata. Sundmus võtab jaburnaljaka poorde, kui mees keskendub erinevate seadmete ja meetodite loomisele, mis poorab terve pere elu pea peale.

programme.title: Ein Tag Wildnis
programme.desc: Üks oopaev - see on vaid silmapilk. Ent uheainsa paeva jooksul toimuvad looduses suured muutused. Naeme lõputut ilu ja pidevat vastasseisu. Kõik elav peegeldab paikese ja kuu igapaevast rannakut ule taevavõlvi. Üks paev võib muuta kõike!

programme.title: Pool sajandit varske Apelsin
programme.desc: Ansambel Apelsin on veerenud pool sajandit koos erinevate solistide, laulukirjutajate ja isegi riigikordadega. Mismoodi see kirju seltskond Eesti muusikat igaveseks muutis, lahkavad Ivo Linna, Harry Kõrvits, Olavi Pihlamagi, Ants Nuut, Helin-Mari Arder, Mart ja Martin Aare ning teised. Toimetajad Kai Vaartnõu ja Karmel Killandi, režissoor Hanna Šein-Meier, operaator Rasmus Kosseson, produtsent Kadi Katarina Priske. 27. septembril on Ants Nuudil 75. sunnipaev. Palju õnne!

programme.title: Aktuaalne kaamera
programme.desc: Alaliselt jarelvaadatav

programme.title: Eesti mang
programme.desc: Sel nadalal on esindatud peagi uues majas hooaega alustav Tallinna Linnateater koosseisus Maris Nõlvak, Mart Toome ja Simo Andre Kadastu. Saadet juhib Gaute Kivistik.

programme.title: Meie kirjanduse lugu
programme.desc: Ester Kuntu vahendab lugusid Eesti kirjanikest ja analuusib nendega meie proosa ning luule tippteoseid. Neljandas osas jõuame valja tanapaeva. Kõneleme Lennart Meri fenomenist poliitikas, kaime kulas Leelo Tunglal ja tema tutrel Maarja Kangrol ning meenutame Kauksi Ülle ja Urmas Vadiga poorast aastatuhandevahetust Tartus. Sari sundis Eesti Kirjanike Liidu 100. sunnipaevaks. Toimetaja Kai Vaartnõu, konsultant Anu Tonts, režissoor Raivo Maripuu, produtsent Hannela Lippus.

programme.title: Ühe pere muusika
programme.desc: Tõnis Magi on laulja, kes tunneb end uhtviisi hasti kontsertareenil kui ka teatrilaval. Samas pole ta lihtsalt artist, vaid tundlik looja, kes hindab looduse vaikust ja vee kohinat. Kohtume Tõnis Magi ja tema kaasa Kart Johansoniga paari romantilises Peedu kodus, mis on tais muusikat, loovust ning aega iseendale.

programme.title: Sport. Sport
programme.desc: Sport. Sport

programme.title: Sisi
programme.desc: Linda vahistatakse kahtlustatuna oma ema mõrvas. Sissi puuab tema suutust tõestada ja palub sõbralt selleks abi. Ludovika veenab Georgi võiduajamisest loobuma. Louis ja Henriette ei suuda teineteisest loobuda. Sophie Charlotte vaevleb armupiinades, sest kuningas Ludwig ei naita tema vastu ules mingit huvi.

programme.title: Miekkailija
programme.desc: 1952. aastal saabub Haapsallu kehalise kasvatuse õpetajaks introvertne meistersportlane Leningradist. Vaatamata koolidirektori vastuseisule hakkab ta lastele vehklemist õpetama. Konarlikust algusest hoolimata saab sõjajargsel raskel ajal vehklemisest teraapia nii lastele kui ka treenerile. Luuasaanud direktorile ei anna aga rahu, miks noormees tegelikult vaikelinna saabus. “Vehkleja” põhineb osaliselt Eesti sportlase ja treeneri Endel Nelise (1925-1993) elulool. Auhinnad: German Cinema Award for Peace - The Bridge 2015; eriauhind Pimedate Öode filmifestival (Tallinn, Eesti) 2015, Tridensi Eesti filmiauhind; EU Film Festival (Ottawa, Canada) 2015, publikuauhind. R: Klaus Haro. O: Mart Avandi, Ursula Ratasepp, Hendrik Toompere, Jaak Prints, Kirill Karo, Lembit Ulfsak jt. Draama. 28. septembril on Endel Nelise 100. sunniaastapaev.

programme.title: Eestlane, atleetide kuningas
programme.desc: Miks on just 10-võistlus Eesti labi aegade edukaim spordiala? Vahur Kersna teledokumentaal otsib vastust labi meie selle ala suurimate heeroste ja nende saatuste. Režissoor Andres Lepasar, produtsent Ruth Heinmaa

programme.title: Blue Lights
programme.desc: Aasta aega ametipostil olnud meeskond peab pistma rinda narkokuritegude lainega, mis tekitab kokkupuuteid lojalistidega. Vagivaldse kokkupõrke tõttu on Stevie ja Gracei toosuhe ohus.

programme.title: Osooni lood
programme.desc: Tarmo Mikussaar portreteerib Eestis uliharuldast lendoravat, kelle kaekaigule on saatuslikuks saanud elupaikade vahenemine.

programme.title: Meie kirjanduse lugu
programme.desc: Saatesari vahendab Ester Kuntu lugusid Eesti kirjanikest ja analuusib nendega meie proosa ning luule tippteoseid. Kolmandas osas, mis keskendub Stalini surma jargsele ajale Eestis, kaime kulas Jaan Krossi ja Ellen Niidu tootoas. Piret Raud meenutab lapsepõlve Kirjanike Majas. Kersti Kreismann jagab uhist elu Mati Undiga ning Kristiina Ehin vahendab lugusid oma isast Andres Ehinist ja Artur Alliksaarest. Sari sundis Eesti Kirjanike Liidu 100. sunnipaevaks. Toimetaja Kai Vaartnõu, konsultant Anu Tonts, režissoor Raivo Maripuu, produtsent Hannela Lippus.

programme.title: Lahutus Eesti moodi
programme.desc: Laura ja Aksel on otsustanud pulmad ara jatta, sest kallis pulmaplaan kaib neile ule jõu. Mirjamil on pommuudis, ta ootab nuud pariselt last ja peab sellest Taunole raakima. Lapse isaks on vahepeal kohatud joogatreener. Kuidas võib see uudis majandusmuredest muserdatud Taunole mõjuda? Laura ja Aksel testivad oma tundeid teineteise vastu ja leiavad ullatudes, et kõik on veel alles. Nuud aga selgub, et Laural on Akslile varuks suur ullatus, mis võib ka pulmaplaani paasta. Stsenarist Martin Algus, režissoor Ergo Kuld, tootja Kassikuld OÜ.

programme.title: Ühe pere muusika
programme.desc: Tõnis Magi on laulja, kes tunneb end uhtviisi hasti kontsertareenil kui ka teatrilaval. Samas pole ta lihtsalt artist, vaid tundlik looja, kes hindab looduse vaikust ja vee kohinat. Kohtume Tõnis Magi ja tema kaasa Kart Johansoniga paari romantilises Peedu kodus, mis on tais muusikat, loovust ning aega iseendale.

programme.title: Hommik Anuga
programme.desc: Hea tuju ja mõnus meeleolu. Ootamatud vaatenurgad ja lahedad nostalgialaksud! Saatejuht Anu Valba. Režissoor Rene Vilbre, produtsent Andres Arro.

programme.title: Muusikast Mihkel Rauaga
programme.desc: Eesti muusikaelus on meile palju uhtekuuluvushetki loonud mitte-eestlastest artistid. Kui keeruline või kerge on eestlaste sudameisse murda muusikul, keda on kultuuriliselt keeruline eestlaseks nimetada? Mihkel Raua vestluskaaslasteks sel teemal on Stefan Airapetjan, Dave Benton, Tanja Mihhailova- Saar, Art Nurhan, Yasmyn, Alar Kotkas, Renee Meriste, Auris Ratsep jt.

programme.title: Miekkailija
programme.desc: 1952. aastal saabub Haapsallu kehalise kasvatuse õpetajaks introvertne meistersportlane Leningradist. Vaatamata koolidirektori vastuseisule hakkab ta lastele vehklemist õpetama. Konarlikust algusest hoolimata saab sõjajargsel raskel ajal vehklemisest teraapia nii lastele kui ka treenerile. Luuasaanud direktorile ei anna aga rahu, miks noormees tegelikult vaikelinna saabus. “Vehkleja” põhineb osaliselt Eesti sportlase ja treeneri Endel Nelise (1925-1993) elulool. Auhinnad: German Cinema Award for Peace - The Bridge 2015; eriauhind Pimedate Öode filmifestival (Tallinn, Eesti) 2015, Tridensi Eesti filmiauhind; EU Film Festival (Ottawa, Canada) 2015, publikuauhind. R: Klaus Haro. O: Mart Avandi, Ursula Ratasepp, Hendrik Toompere, Jaak Prints, Kirill Karo, Lembit Ulfsak jt. Draama. 28. septembril on Endel Nelise 100. sunniaastapaev.

programme.title: The Secret Life Of The Zoo
programme.desc: Kaelkirjak Kidepo viiakse teise loomaaeda, ent suure looma kolimine on ohtlik ulesanne. Hõbegibon Alvin soovib tagasi kaasa juurde minna, ent poeg surmab kire. Juhtisasest tuugasseale esitatakse valjakutse ja ei jaa muud ule kui konkurent Saksamaale kolida.

programme.title: Karen Pirie
programme.desc: 1984. aastal rooviti naftamagnaadi tutar koos vaikse pojaga. 2024. aastal leitakse karjaarist laip, mis juhatab otse selle ammuse roovi juurde. Nuud on Karen Piriel aeg oma meeskonnaga see vana lugu lõplikult lahendada.

programme.title: Maahommik
programme.desc: "Maahommik" randab mooda Eestimaad ringi ja kohtub erinevate inimeste ja nende põnevate tegemistega. Teie ees rullub lahti maaelu varvipalett koos kõikide oma varjunditega. Loomad, taimed, talud, tood ja musttuhat muud lugu ootab teid just "Maahommiku" saates. Saatejuht on Kerli Dello. Vastutav toimetaja Maili Metssalu, režissoorid Mikk Mae ja Mati Kark, produtsent Tiina-Mari Koljak.

programme.title: Impulss
programme.desc: Tanavu moodub parvlaev Estonia hukust 30 aastat. Kusime, kas nuud on lõpuks kaes aeg uurimistega rahu teha? Saatejuhid on Anna Pihl ja Joosep Vark, produtsent Mai Kangro.

programme.title: IT-vaatlik
programme.desc: Kubermaailma võlusid kasutades võime sattuda erinevate pahatahtlike kavatsuste ohvriks. Kuidas parandada kuberturvalisust, margata ohumarke ja ennetada võimalikku kahju? Praktilist nõu, kuidas internetis turvaliselt toimetada, petukirju ara tunda, sotsiaalmeedias mõistlikult kaituda ja palju muud, jagavad oma ala spetsialistid.

programme.title: TeadusEST
programme.desc: Teaduse tegemine on meeskonnatoo, kuid vahel peab see tiim koosnema sadadest või tuhandetest inimestest, et jõuda suurte avastusteni. Selle suure meeskonna võivad moodustada ka taiesti tavalised inimesed. Selleks võib olla arhiivifotode korrastamine või metsise seire, aga ka tolmurullide või puukide teadlastele saatmine. “TeadusEST” tutvustab sel korral harrastusteadlasi ja teadusprojekte, kus igauks saab kaasa luua teaduse tegemisse. Saatejuht-toimetaja Kristjan Pihl, toimetaja Liisi Molder, režissoor Liis Lindmaa, produtsent Anatoli Tafitšuk, tootja Ulm Production. Saade valmib koostoos Eesti Teadusagentuuriga.

programme.title: Aktuaalne kaamera
programme.desc: Alaliselt jarelvaadatav

programme.title: Ukraina stuudio
programme.desc: "Ukraina stuudio" võtab kokku Venemaa-Ukraina sõja viimased arengud. Saates antakse hinnang nadala jooksul sõjatandril toimunule, arutletakse võimalike edasiste sõjaliste ja poliitiliste arengute ule ning kaalutakse sõja mõju erinevatele valdkondadele. Stuudios astuvad koos saatejuhtidega ules eksperdid.

programme.title: Klassikatahed
programme.desc: Kauaoodatud muusikute konkurss „Klassikatahed“ on tagasi, et tuua televaatajate ette kuus saravat artisti ja naidata, mida noored talendid oma pilliga teha suudavad. Kes on parim? Kes saravaim? Kellel on rohkem õnne? „Klassikataht 2025“ selgub juba kuue nadala parast. Esimeses saates esitavad võistlejad koos Tallinna Kammerorkestriga maailmamuusika kaunimaid meloodiaid. Kas võistlejate esitused poevad hinge ja liigutavad pisarateni ka muusikaproffidest žuriid? Saate kohtunikeks on dirigendid Paavo Jarvi ja Risto Joost ning maailmalavadel tuntud bariton Lauri Vasar. Saadet juhib pianist Johan Randvere. Formaadi autorid on Helen Valkna, Anu Valba ja Timo Steiner, saate režissoor Krista Luts. Konkurss „Klassikatahed“ sunnib Eesti Televisiooni, Klassikaraadio, Eesti Kontserdi ning Kultuuripartnerlus SA koostoos.

programme.title: Teemaõhtu
programme.desc: Mart Juure 60. juubelisunnipaeva puhul vestleb temaga hea sõber Peeter Oja. Juttu tuleb nii elust kui ka inimestest, nii muusikast kui ka huumorist. Saates ei raagita maksukuuru kaotamisest, tumeainest ja meretuuleparkidest. Režissoor Rene Vilbre, toimetaja Anu Valba, produtsent Laura-Liisa Veiler. 29. septembril on Mart Juurel 61. sunnipaev. Palju õnne!

programme.title: Hercule Poirot
programme.desc: Õhtusoogil Poirot sõbra ja endise naitleja juures kukub nailiselt põhjuseta kokku kohalik kirikuõpetaja. Isegi Poirot ei kahtlusta midagi, kuni toimub uus õhtusook tapselt sama seltskonnaga ja taas sureb uks kulalistest.

programme.title: Hommik Anuga
programme.desc: Hea tuju ja mõnus meeleolu. Ootamatud vaatenurgad ja lahedad nostalgialaksud! Saatejuht Anu Valba. Režissoor Rene Vilbre, produtsent Andres Arro.

programme.title: Nullpunkt
programme.desc: Kooli kulastab tuntud muusikaprodutsent ja Johannes pakub talle oma laulusõnu. Kodus tekivad poisi ja ema vahel pinged. Klassis levivad Johannese kohta kuulujutud ja peagi saab ta aru, et terve klass vihkab teda.

programme.title: Amazing Race Suomi
programme.desc: Kilpailijat suuntaavat luonnon helmaan ja hivuttautuvat vaijeria myoden jattimaisen luolaston ylapuolelle. Tama vaatii niin rohkeutta kuin voimaa, ja yksi kisaaja on pahasti pulassa. Paikalliset traditiot tulevat tutuksi riisipellolla, jossa hurjat ihmisharat katkaisevat tiimien tien. Mudantahrimat kilpailijat istuvat lopuksi soittimien aareen ja haastavat itsensa mahdottomalta tuntuvan tehtavan edessa.

programme.title: Korkeasaari
programme.desc: Nyt kurkistetaan kulissien taakse ja nahdaan, miten Korkeasaaren Kissojen Yo rakentuu. Manuleilla on omat kiireensa uusien pentujen kanssa ja niiden nimeaminen Q-kirjaimen mukaan ei ole helpoin homma hoitajille. Perinteisen Kissojen Yon lisaksi piipahdetaan ensimmaista kertaa jarjestettavassa, ainoastaan aikuisille suunnatussa tapahtumassa.

programme.title: Tahdet, tahdet
programme.desc: On aika laittaa lanteet keinumaan ja hypata varikkaaseen lattarien maailmaan. Kilpailijat nostavat lavalle tulisia rytmeja kielenkannat paukkuen, perinteikasta bossanovaa unohtamatta. Illan aikana koetaan myos ketsuppipullon kokoinen yllatys, kolmen sanan mittainen esitys, seka toinen toistaan nayttavampia tanssiesityksia. Lopussa jannitetaan, kuka esiintyjista joutuu jaHamaan kilpailun.

programme.title: Tahdet, tahdet
programme.desc: Äitienpaivan kunniaksi kilpailijat tekevat hyvaa Pelastakaa Lasten kanssa ja esittavat kauneimpia rakkauslauluja jousikvartetin saestaessa. Silmat eivat pysy kuivina, kun kilpailijat nakevat tarinoita aidinrakkaudesta Ukrainassa ja muilla kriisialueilla. Myos kilpailu kiristyy, kun yksi esiintyja putoaa kisasta illan paatteeksi. Katsojat voivat auttaa lapsia kriiseissa osallistumalla Pelastakaa Lasten keraykseen Tahdet, tahdet -kauden loppuun asti. Kotimainen musiikkiohjelma.

programme.title: Maryn helpot kokkailut
programme.desc: Mary esittelee parhaat grillireseptit. Han valmistaa lohikebabeja misopaallisella, kurttukaalia sinihomejuustolla, grillattua sangriaa ja herkullisen kokonaisena grillatun kanan.

programme.title: Farmi Suomi
programme.desc: Farmin arki pyorahtaa seuraavalle vaihteelle, kun kilpailijat saavat yha haastavampia tehtavia, ja samaan aikaan syntyy kuppikuntia. Tunteiden vuoristorata on todellinen, kun tehtavat ja nimeamiset jannittavat kilpailijoita. Areenalla nahdaan, kuka laittaa jauhot ja kenen suuhun.

programme.title: Lomakoti auringon alta
programme.desc: Kausi 1. Jakso 10/20. Salerno. Kolmikko lahtee ajamaan pitkin sateista Salernoa lahella Amalfin rannikkoa Italiassa. Kukin etsii perhelomakohdetta, mutta Sam haluaa tehda vaikutuksen 70-luvun biletalolla. Sen sijaan Amandan kohde on taynna ihania herkkuja. Englantilainen lifestyleohjelma.

programme.title: Savotta
programme.desc: Savotta on seurantareality ihmisista, jotka elavat metsasta. He ovat metsureita, metsakoneenkuljettajia ja metsaalan yrittajia, joiden paivittainen tyo ja arki vievat katsojan metsanhoidon vaativiin tehtaviin ja sen arvaamattomiin olosuhteisiin. Sarjassa avataan lisaksi puukaupan monivaiheista prosessia seka ostajan etta myyjan nakokulmasta. Mukana nahdaan keihaanheiton moninkertaiset arvokisamitalistit Tero Pitkamaki ja Antti Ruuskanen, jotka ovat hypanneet rohkeasti uudelle uralle metsaalan yrittajina. Sarjaan he lahtivat mukaan, koska halusivat tuoda nostetta ja nakyvyytta metsaalalle. Kuusiosaisessa sarjassa seurataan eri puolella Suomea tyoskentelevia metsaalan ammattilaisia ja opiskelijoita, joita kaikkia yhdistaa aito yhteys luontoon, seka tyossa etta vapaa-ajalla.

programme.title: NCIS Rikostutkijat
programme.desc: Kausi 22. Jakso 14/20. Lampiman huumorin savyttamassa rikosdraamasarjassa seurataan Yhdysvaltain laivaston erikoisyksikkoa, jonka tehtavana on selvittaa eri puolilla maailmaa rikoksia, jotka tavalla tai toisella liittyvat Yhdysvaltain laivastoon tai merijalkavakeen. Taitavaa ja monipuolista tiimia johtaa Mark Harmonin esittama agentti Gibbs. Paaosissa ovat: Mark Harmon, David McCallum, Pauley Perrette ja Sean Murray. Amerikkalainen rikosdraamasarja.

programme.title: NCIS Rikostutkijat
programme.desc: Kausi 22. Jakso 15/20. Kuutamolla. NCIS-agentti Sawyer proystailee uudella autollaan, mika kummastuttaa Nickia. Pian kuolleena loytynyt luutnantti kietoutuu tapahtumaketjuun. Amerikkalainen rikosdraamasarja.

programme.title: Arman Pohjantahden alla
programme.desc: Miten toimii suomalainen vankeinlaitos, parantaako vai pahentaako vankila ihmista? Arman vie katsojan suljettujen ovien ja kylmien katseiden taakse ja pohtii vapauden seka oikeuksien menettamista.

programme.title: Amazing Race Suomi
programme.desc: Kausi 1. Jakso 10/12. Hindutemppeli haastaa kisaajat loputtomine portaineen, ja laskutoimitus osoittautuu yllattavan vaikeaksi. Apina varastaa temppelilahjan, ja munkin etsiminen luolastosta aiheuttaa hammentavia hetkia. Tuhannet kirjat pistavat kilpailijoiden paan sekaisin, eika yksi tiimi meinaa millaan loytaa oikeaa opusta. Tunnelma tiivistyy tien paalla, kun kaikki keinot otetaan kayttoon. Kotimainen realitysarja.

programme.title: Amazing Race Suomi
programme.desc: Tiimit hyppaavat junaan ja suuntaavat kohti pohjoista. Vanhankaupungin kujilla etsitaan kuumeisesti katutaidetta ja anellaan paikallisia yhteisiin kuviin. Itamainen teatteritaide puskee kilpailijat epamukavuusalueelle, jossa kaydaan hyvan ja pahan taistelu. Kun kakkupalat eivat loyda oikeaa muotoaan, kuumenevat yhden tiimin tunteet toden teolla.

programme.title: Korkeasaari
programme.desc: Karhut alkavat valmistella talvipesiaan, vaikka talvi ei tunnu edes alkaneen. Tapaamme myos Korkeasaaren uuden gasellipukin ja naemme, mita leijona tekee benji-koydella. Lisaksi tarkistetaan Villielainsairaalassa hoidossa olevan ilveksen hampaan tilanne, josta ei selvita ilman nukutusta.

programme.title: Tahdet, tahdet
programme.desc: Kuusi kilpailijaa on selvittanyt tiensa kohti kiristyvaa loppusuoraa. Tanaan nostalgisoidaan leffaklassikoiden ja tv-tunnarien parissa. Toiset ovat valinneet esitettavakseen koskettavia ikivihreita, kun taas toiset lahestyvat aihetta humoristisemmalla otteella. Kuka hurmaa tuomaristossa istuvat Juuso Makilahteen, Lilli Paasikiven ja Sami Yaffan, kuka laulaa tiensa studioyleison sydamiin ja kenen matka Tahdet, tahdet -lavalla paattyy?

programme.title: Tahdet, tahdet
programme.desc: On aika kaivaa esiin festarimuistot seka hiekkateilla kiitavat mopedit ja painaa kaasua, silla tassa jaksossa Tahdet, tahdet -kilpailijat tuovat lavalle kesan! Illan aikana pyorahdetaan diskon pyorteissa, takerrutaan kesahittien korvamatoihin ja rajaytellaan paukkuja, kuin kesailtana konsanaan. Artistit puhaltavat yhteen hiileen ja avaavat illan kesaisen yhteiskappaleen voimin. Ketka kilpailijoista selvittavat tiensa kohti seuraavan viikon semifinaalia?

programme.title: Maryn helpot kokkailut
programme.desc: Kausi 1. Jakso 1/25. Kanaa neljalla tavalla. Mary esittelee nelja niin helppoa kanareseptia, ettei huonoimmallakaan kokilla mene sormi suuhun. Han valmistaa mehevan kokonaisen kanan, lohduttavaa kananuudelikeittoa ja mausteista kanawokkia. Jopa parmesaanikana valmistuu helposti ja ilman hassakkaa. Kanadalainen ruokareality.

programme.title: Farmi Suomi
programme.desc: Elaimet tuovat farmilaisille lohtua, pelkoa ja lisatyota, eika aikaakaan, kun lisaa karvaisia tulokkaita saapuu maatilalle. Uusi torppari saa farmilaiset repeamaan liitoksistaan, silla yllattava torpparinvalinta vaikuttaa niin tehtavista suoriutumiseen kuin kuppikuntien kokoonpanoihin.

programme.title: Lomakoti auringon alta
programme.desc: Kausi 1. Jakso 11/20. Saint-Émilion. Nyt tutustutaan maaseudun lomakoteihin Saint-Émilionissa, joka sijaitsee viinialueella. Kaikki juontajat eivat kuitenkaan noudata ohjeistusta. Lisaksi nahdaan upeita, mutta myos omintakeisia sisustusratkaisuja. Englantilainen lifestyleohjelma.

programme.title: Savotta
programme.desc: Kauden paatosjaksossa opiskelijat pohtivat tulevaisuuden suunnitelmiaan. Kittilassa metsakoneet seisovat kovan pakkasen vuoksi. Annastiina jarjestaa esittelykierrosta puunkasittelyn tehtaalle. Antti suunnittelee metsapalstan ostoa ja Tero kannustaa lapsiaan hiihtokilpailuissa. Metsureilla pitaa kiiretta runkolinjaa uhkaavien puiden kanssa. Lahde mukaan suomalaisen metsan siimekseen!

programme.title: Tulossa: Temptation Island Suomi (12)
programme.desc: Tulossa Nelonen Median kanavilla. Kotimainen ohjelma.

programme.title: NCIS Rikostutkijat
programme.desc: NCIS-tiimi on lahtemassa viettamaan vapaailtaa kukin tavallaan, mutta tyot eivat jata tiimilaisia rauhaan, kun tulipalossa kuollut ylikersantti paljastuukin murhan uhriksi.

programme.title: NCIS Rikostutkijat
programme.desc: Kausi 22. Jakso 17/20. Lampiman huumorin savyttamassa rikosdraamasarjassa seurataan Yhdysvaltain laivaston erikoisyksikkoa, jonka tehtavana on selvittaa eri puolilla maailmaa rikoksia, jotka tavalla tai toisella liittyvat Yhdysvaltain laivastoon tai merijalkavakeen. Taitavaa ja monipuolista tiimia johtaa Mark Harmonin esittama agentti Gibbs. Paaosissa ovat: Mark Harmon, David McCallum, Pauley Perrette ja Sean Murray. Amerikkalainen rikosdraamasarja.

programme.title: Arman Pohjantahden alla
programme.desc: Missa viettaa yonsa koditon ihminen tai mista koyha saa seuraavan ateriansa? Arman kohtaa yhteiskuntamme vahaosaisimmat ja kysyy, miten hyvinvointivaltiossa voi joutua kadulle ja leipajonon jatkeeksi?

programme.title: Amazing Race Suomi
programme.desc: Finaalietappi kaynnistyy, ja tiimit ryntaavat kohti viimeisia haasteita. Satamassa kiivetaan korkeaan nosturiin, joka verottaa kilpailijoiden voimia rankalla kadella. Teen moninaiset maut pistavat paan pyoralle, ja katuvilinassa suunnistaminen vetaa hermot kirealle. Tanssin saloihin sukelletaan leijonan vaatteissa, ja monimutkainen koreografia tuntuu mahdottomalta oppia. Kun kuula ponnahtaa taivaalle, on kotiinlahdon aika. Helsingissa selviaa, mika tiimi ehtii matolle ensimmaisena ja voittaa 30 000 euroa!

programme.title: Det ar overnaturligt!
programme.desc: Bibelns hosthogtider och den yttersta tiden. Perry Stone talar om betydelsen av Bibelns hogtider och varfor hostens hogtider ar viktiga nu nar tiden narmar sig sitt slut. Han delar en viktig uppenbarelse som visar att den yttersta tiden ar har.

programme.title: Att hora Guds rost
programme.desc: Hur talar Gud idag?. Om Gud vill tala till mig och jag kan hora Honom, var ska jag borja? Hur talar Gud egentligen i dag? Och var kommer Bibeln in? Med Nohadra Heido, Christer Dahlberg, Veikko Luukkonen och Celebre Binua.

programme.title: Boneskola
programme.desc: Håll fast i Guds svar nar du ber. Jehova Roi – Herren min herde. Ge problemet till Gud och se vad Han har att saga om vår utmaning och vilken losning Han bereder åt oss.

programme.title: Cafe Bibeln Uppsala
programme.desc: Hur ska vi hålla missionen levande?. Varfor ska vi missionera, for vem och av vem? Och gor bibeloversattningar skillnad nar vi lyder missionsbefallningen? Leif Nummela samtalar med Mats-Jan Soderberg från organisationen Folk och språk.

programme.title: Pilgrim Media
programme.desc: Vi står infor ett vagval. Josef Lowdin undervisar om varfor det ar fel med den breda ekumeniken och att vi måste valja vilken vag vi skall ta. Den ekumeniska vagen eller trohet till Guds Ord?

programme.title: Aktuellt från Mellanostern
programme.desc: Tvåstatsmodellen. Palestina, vad ar det som nationerna erkanner egentligen? Och leder dessa proklamationer nu till fred?

programme.title: Trons grunder med Åke Carlson
programme.desc: Bibeln - Guds eget Ord till oss. Grunderna for den kristna tron hittar vi i Bibeln, Guds eget Ord, som ar ofelbart och sant, aven historiskt. Bibeln uppenbarar Guds egenskaper och lar oss forstå Hans fralsningsplan med manniskan.

programme.title: Letters
programme.desc: I serien Letters får vi i en kreativ brevform av ljud och bild ta del av ett antal manniskors personliga upplevelser med Gud.

programme.desc: TV7 Israelnyheter

programme.title: Två grannar
programme.desc: Vagen ut i larjungaskap. Magnus och Pia fick en profetisk halsning som forandrade deras satt att resonera och ledde dem in i en relation med Jesus.

programme.title: Upptack livet
programme.desc: Den befriande Guden. Vi ar slavar under synden. Kan vi bli fria? Precis som Gud befriade Israels folk från farao och slaveriet i Egypten befriar Han oss från våra egna slavdrivande gudar.

programme.title: LUMO - Johannesevangeliet
programme.desc: Johannes 15:1-16:15. Dramatisering av evangelietexten på svenska. Jesus ar vagen till Fadern. Jesus lovar sanda Hjalparen

programme.title: Davids slunga
programme.desc: En Goliat till. Nar den forsta striden var over levde David inte lycklig i alla sina dagar bara sådar. Nej, flera hinder och fiender fick han mota, men alla verkade ha dåliga dagar i motet med Davids Herre och Gud.

programme.title: Lovsångens språk
programme.desc: Arild Måso. Arild Måso ar same och lovsjunger Gud på samiskt vis. Detta har lett till att han stott på mycket motstånd, men samtidigt har han fått nå ut till urbefolkningen i hela varlden med evangeliet.

programme.title: Israel talar
programme.desc: Sakerhetsstaketet och dess verkningar. På sommaren 2012 har det gått 10 år sedan Israels regering beslot bygga det valkanda sakerhetsstaketet. programme.title: TV7 Israelnyheter
programme.desc: TV7 Israelnyheter

programme.title: Två grannar
programme.desc: Vagen ut i larjungaskap. Magnus och Pia fick en profetisk halsning som forandrade deras satt att resonera och ledde dem in i en relation med Jesus.

programme.title: Upptack livet
programme.desc: Den befriande Guden. Vi ar slavar under synden. Kan vi bli fria? Precis som Gud befriade Israels folk från farao och slaveriet i Egypten befriar Han oss från våra egna slavdrivande gudar.

programme.title: LUMO - Johannesevangeliet
programme.desc: Johannes 15:1-16:15. Dramatisering av evangelietexten på svenska. Jesus ar vagen till Fadern. Jesus lovar sanda Hjalparen

programme.title: Davids slunga
programme.desc: En Goliat till. Nar den forsta striden var over levde David inte lycklig i alla sina dagar bara sådar. Nej, flera hinder och fiender fick han mota, men alla verkade ha dåliga dagar i motet med Davids Herre och Gud.

programme.title: Lovsångens språk
programme.desc: Arild Måso. Arild Måso ar same och lovsjunger Gud på samiskt vis. Detta har lett till att han stott på mycket motstånd, men samtidigt har han fått nå ut till urbefolkningen i hela varlden med evangeliet.

programme.title: Israel talar
programme.desc: Sakerhetsstaketet och dess verkningar. På sommaren 2012 har det gått 10 år sedan Israels regering beslot bygga det valkanda sakerhetsstaketet. Fastan arbetet inte ar slutfort, ar det redan nu det dyraste projektet i Israels historia. De ekonomiska foljderna ar andå små i jamforelse med de politiska foljderna.

programme.title: Det ar overnaturligt!
programme.desc: Bibelns hosthogtider och den yttersta tiden. Perry Stone talar om betydelsen av Bibelns hogtider och varfor hostens hogtider ar viktiga nu nar tiden narmar sig sitt slut. Han delar en viktig uppenbarelse som visar att den yttersta tiden ar har.

programme.title: Att hora Guds rost
programme.desc: Hur talar Gud idag?. Om Gud vill tala till mig och jag kan hora Honom, var ska jag borja? Hur talar Gud egentligen i dag? Och var kommer Bibeln in? Med Nohadra Heido, Christer Dahlberg, Veikko Luukkonen och Celebre Binua.

programme.title: Boneskola
programme.desc: Håll fast i Guds svar nar du ber. Jehova Roi – Herren min herde. Ge problemet till Gud och se vad Han har att saga om vår utmaning och vilken losning Han bereder åt oss.

programme.title: Cafe Bibeln Uppsala
programme.desc: Hur ska vi hålla missionen levande?. Varfor ska vi missionera, for vem och av vem? Och gor bibeloversattningar skillnad nar vi lyder missionsbefallningen? Leif Nummela samtalar med Mats-Jan Soderberg från organisationen Folk och språk.

programme.title: Pilgrim Media
programme.desc: Vi står infor ett vagval. Josef Lowdin undervisar om varfor det ar fel med den breda ekumeniken och att vi måste valja vilken vag vi skall ta. Den ekumeniska vagen eller trohet till Guds Ord?

programme.title: Aktuellt från Mellanostern
programme.desc: Tvåstatsmodellen. Palestina, vad ar det som nationerna erkanner egentligen? Och leder dessa proklamationer nu till fred?

programme.title: Trons grunder med Åke Carlson
programme.desc: Bibeln - Guds eget Ord till oss. Grunderna for den kristna tron hittar vi i Bibeln, Guds eget Ord, som ar ofelbart och sant, aven historiskt. Bibeln uppenbarar Guds egenskaper och lar oss forstå Hans fralsningsplan med manniskan.

programme.title: Kristet Center Örebro
programme.desc: Ta vara på accelerationen. Bara vi forstår att vara tillgangliga for Gud och de uppgifter Han vill ge oss kan vi snabbt sprida de goda nyheterna. Tommy Hagsten undervisar om att ta vara på det ord som gått ut.

programme.title: Rakt på sak med Ingemar Helmner
programme.desc: Verklig folkkyrka. Ingemar Helmner beskriver den idealiska forsamlingen - den som forenar folkkyrka med vackelsekyrka. Dar kyrkan inte ar en stelnad forening utan en oppen spontan famn som alltid predikar fralsning.

programme.title: Homes of Hope - aktiva kristna hem
programme.desc: Dela din berattelse. Hur blir vi aktiva i att nå manniskor med evangeliet i vår vardag? Patrik Sandberg ger praktiska tips kring hur vi kan dela vår berattelse, be om Guds ledning och formedla HOPP till vår omgivning.

programme.title: Aktuellt från Mellanostern
programme.desc: Tvåstatsmodellen. Palestina, vad ar det som nationerna erkanner egentligen? Och leder dessa proklamationer nu till fred?

programme.title: Gamla Testamentet oppnas
programme.desc: Samuel 1 och 2. 1/2. Pawson berattar i detta avsnitt om profeten Samuel samt om Israels forsta kungar, Saul och David. Pawson faster speciell vikt vid upp- och nedgångarna i deras liv, och hur dessa påverkades av deras forhållande till Gud.

programme.title: Valsignade samtal - om vardagssjalavård
programme.desc: Identitet och två olika satt att leva. Det finns två vagar enligt Boris Salo – A-vagen och V-vagen. Vad ar detta for vagar och på vilket satt spelar de roll i min sjalvbild och identitet?

programme.title: Guldkorn - Tillsammans ber vi
programme.desc: Saliga ar de som skapar frid. Marie Skogvard undervisar om konflikthantering: ett viktigt verktyg som hjalper oss att bevara våra relationer, i enlighet med Guds Ord. Ur Tillsammans ber vi LIVE 103.

programme.title: Argument for tro
programme.desc: Det kosmologiska argumentet for Guds existens. Har universum alltid existerat? Eller har det kommit till någon gång? Har det någon betydelse i så fall?

programme.title: Kungen kommer
programme.desc: Alija - uppfyllelsen och Guds rike. Folket Israels återvandande ar en central del i Guds rikes manifestation på jorden. Forstår det judiska folket sin roll i Guds rikes ankomst har och nu? Forstår forsamlingen det judiska folkets roll?

programme.title: Vandpunkten
programme.desc: Karlek till varje pris. I programmet får vi hora om risker med graviditet for svarta kvinnor, sångaren Naomi Raines nya soloprojekt och en kvinna vars karlek i livet ledde henne till år i fangelse.

programme.title: Dina relationer
programme.desc: Befrielse. Befrielse ar något som Gud vardesatter hogt och vill ge oss alla manniskor. Mats Nyholm undervisar, med inledande vittnesbord av Kjell Edstrom.

programme.title: TV7 Israel - Brodernas forsvarare
programme.desc: Forsamlingen i Turkiet – i historien och i vår tid. Michael Kerem talar i dag med bibellararen Jerry Mattix om Turkiet, vars geografiska område blev centralt for de forsta kristna. Hurdant ar laget for de turkiska forsamlingarna i dag?

programme.desc: Tro och ekonomi. Hur forholl sig den tidiga kristna forsamlingen till pengar och egendom? Hur bor vi gora det?
